<h3 id="default">Manage default zone</h3>	
<p>Default zone is the main zone which is applied to shipping and taxation if no defined zones are available / applicable.</p>	

<p>Shipping rates - rates that determine variuos pricing according to order's weight or value. To add a new shipping <ins>service?</ins>:</p>

<ul>
	<li>Name - the name of the shipping service (for example, "Extra heavy")</li>
	<li>Select "Weight based calculation" or "Subtotal based calculation".</li>
	<li>Click the "Add new rate" link and complete the necessary fields to create a rate.</li>
	<li>Translate - if applicable, select a language to translate the name of the service.</li>
	<li>Click the "Save" button.</li>
</ul>

